S.FORM: Fengbin Fengbin gu icuwa i Hualien. ala atjunangn mapuljat 157.26 km² (ma'linpan atjunang 61.89 km², ma'linaule atjunang 12.67 km²). ala caucau mapuljat 4,464 caucau, ala daceneqlan mapuljat 1,704 a daceneqlan, Amis, Kebalan, Sakizaya, Bunun (83%) a maqcuwa caucau. a i pasakacedas ta ljavek; a i pasaviri ta rinahem(shoufeng gu); a i pasanavalj ta kakacawan(changbin gu) na valangaw; a i pasakaledep ta marlimu(fenglin), fata'an(guangfu gu), kohkoh(ruisui gu), kata posko(yuli). izuazua a tjatjuruvu a caucau se amis(pangcah) imaza. izua qinaljan na sakizaya kata kebalan uta. paljavak tua atjunang matja 5 qinaljan i Fengbin. matja 15 qinaljan imaza, Laeno , Makotaay , Tida'an , Kodic , Fakong , Haciliwan , Tingalaw , Tisilan , Tafugan , Cawi , Malaloong , Dipit , Paterungan , Kaluluwan , Culiu . pinaljavakan sipaljavaljavak na sihu a fengbin gu tucu taicu a alu a qinaljan a lima a cun imaza. cinalivatan kasicuayan a kinaizuan a qinaljan na caucau se kacalisian. izua qinaljan imaza a paterungan, makotaay, fakong, kata zumanga. kadjunangan izua qadjav a 162 km2 a kadjunangan imaza i pinaljavakan a fengbin gu. caucau papupaysu tataleman kakiciqavan tatuluan izua lima a gakku a kedrikedri imaza. biuing izua ita a biuing imaza i fengbin gu. iyubingkiuku (yuzeng) sasupuan na iyubingkiuku 977 a sasupuan na iyubingkiku se fengbin. remayurangan sipacacikeljan palidring a djalan sikamasansimuluq saka ita a palidring a djalan na taiwan sikamasansimuluq saka ita-A a palidring a djalan na taiwan(pasakaledep ta sikamasansivalj a palidring a djalan na taiwan) sikamasan 64 a palidring a djalan na kalinku(palidring a djalan a 瑞港) basu sikamasan 1125 a basu na sutu, a kemasi ta ljaljevavavan na fata'an(guangfu) ta kisiya a patjemaza i fakong(fengbin) sikamasan 1140 a basu na kalinku, a kemasi ta kalinku a patje 靜浦 sikamasan 1140-A a basu na kalinku, a kemasi ta kalinku a patje 靜浦 kisiya djalan gungkang hikuki djamay

Fengbin Fengbin go icowa i Hoalien. ala atjonangn mapoljat 157.26 km² (ma'linpan atjonang 61.89 km², ma'linaole atjonang 12.67 km²). ala caocao mapoljat 4,464 caocao, ala daceneqlan mapoljat 1,704 a daceneqlan, Amis, Kebalan, Sakizaya, Bonon (83%) a maqcowa caocao. a i pasakacedas ta ljavek; a i pasaviri ta rinahem(shoofeng go); a i pasanavalj ta kakacawan(changbin go) na valangaw; a i pasakaledep ta marlimo(fenglin), fata'an(goangfo go), kohkoh(roisoi go), kata posko(yoli). izoazoa a tjatjorovo a caocao se amis(pangcah) imaza. izoa qinaljan na sakizaya kata kebalan ota. paljavak toa atjonang matja 5 qinaljan i Fengbin. matja 15 qinaljan imaza, Laeno , Makotaay , Tida'an , Kodic , Fakong , Haciliwan , Tingalaw , Tisilan , Tafogan , Cawi , Malaloong , Dipit , Paterongan , Kalolowan , Colio . pinaljavakan sipaljavaljavak na siho a fengbin go toco taico a alo a qinaljan a lima a con imaza. cinalivatan kasicoayan a kinaizoan a qinaljan na caocao se kacalisian. izoa qinaljan imaza a paterongan, makotaay, fakong, kata zomanga. kadjonangan izoa qadjav a 162 km2 a kadjonangan imaza i pinaljavakan a fengbin go. caocao papopayso tataleman kakiciqavan tatoloan izoa lima a gakko a kedrikedri imaza. bioing izoa ita a bioing imaza i fengbin go. iyobingkioko (yozeng) sasopoan na iyobingkioko 977 a sasopoan na iyobingkiko se fengbin. remayorangan sipacacikeljan palidring a djalan sikamasansimoloq saka ita a palidring a djalan na taiwan sikamasansimoloq saka ita-A a palidring a djalan na taiwan(pasakaledep ta sikamasansivalj a palidring a djalan na taiwan) sikamasan 64 a palidring a djalan na kalinko(palidring a djalan a 瑞港) baso sikamasan 1125 a baso na soto, a kemasi ta ljaljevavavan na fata'an(goangfo) ta kisiya a patjemaza i fakong(fengbin) sikamasan 1140 a baso na kalinko, a kemasi ta kalinko a patje 靜浦 sikamasan 1140-A a baso na kalinko, a kemasi ta kalinko a patje 靜浦 kisiya djalan gongkang hikoki djamay
